title: 209. Andy & DJ CTI: Boosters For Children?, "No More Here" & We The People
itunes:title: 209. Andy & DJ CTI: Boosters For Children?, "No More Here" & We The People
description: In today's episode, Andy and DJ discuss critics questioning President Biden's FDA approval of COVID booster shots for children, two black women being refused service at Nori Japan, and 34% of Americans saying violence against the government is sometimes justified.
